subject: College Athletics
Hockey, Ice
NCAA Ice Hockey Championships
lead_paragraph: Aaron Dell made 26 saves and top-ranked North Dakota routed Denver, 6-1, in the N.C.A.A. Midwest final in Green Bay, Wis., to advance to the Frozen Four.
